dc_description_s: Alternate title: Stadtplan von Exeter mit militaergeographischen Eintragungen. Grossblatt 10, Blattbereich 35. Relief shown by 25 meter contour intervals and spot elevations. Gauss-Krueger grid. Legend is in English and German. With a list of abbreviations. Source: Ordnance Survey 1:10,560; 1935, 1936. Major city access roads are color coded. Accompanied by 24p. booklet: "Militaergeographische Einzelangaben ueber England; Objektbilder zu den militaergeographischen Objektkarten 1:250 000 und 1:10 000 der Mappe 10 Suedwestengland"; of photographs and drawings of important military objectives, bridges, factories, etc. (sites are located on map).
